modName: Craftable Khajiit Earrings Gold and Silver
summary: Earrings for Khajiit craftable at the forge in gold or silver.
descriptionHtml:
I\'ve made the stock Khajiit earrings craftable at the forge and given them new textures. You can craft gold or silver ones. These are made for Khajiit so they will not show up on other races.

I have no intentions of adding to or tweaking this, the only thing I will do is fix bugs or repack it if I was a colossal derp and forgot something.

And no I won\'t take better screenshots. Add some yourself!
author: Deonotte
